import React from "react";
import { Container, Navbar, Nav } from "react-bootstrap";
const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Navbar
      bg="dark"
      expand="sm"
      variant="dark"
      className="position-fixed w-100 "
      style={{ zIndex: "5" }}
    >
      <Container className="">
        {/* <Navbar.Brand href="http://localhost:3000/">HOME</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Brand href="http://localhost:3000/STORE">STORE</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Brand href="http://localhost:3000/ABOUT">ABOUT</Navbar.Brand>
          <Navbar.Brand href="http://localhost:3000/CONTACT">
            CONTACT US
          </Navbar.Brand> */}
        <Nav justify variant="tabs" defaultActiveKey="http://localhost:3000/">
          <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link href="http://localhost:3000/">HOME</Nav.Link>
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="http://localhost:3000/STORE">STORE</Nav.Link>
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="http://localhost:3000/ABOUT">ABOUT</Nav.Link>
          </Nav.Item>
          <Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Link eventKey="http://localhost:3000/CONTACT">
            CONTACT US
            </Nav.Link>
          </Nav.Item>
        </Nav>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
};

export default Header;
